The root issue is caused by bundlers having difficulty tree-shaking classes with `.proprtype.*` accessors. The current status is:

- **rollup**: doesn't support it, [plans to support it](https://twitter.com/lukastaegert/status/1522445453584912384)
- **esbuild**: doesn't support it, [has no intention of supporting it](https://github.com/evanw/esbuild/issues/175#issuecomment-1002787160)
- **webpack**: doesn't support it, no expressed intention


